| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4988 — Recovery Inhibition (werewolves)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8f8daa13-ca8e-501d-bf8f-a5b1eec505d3"
